<DIV align="justify" style="font-size: 10pt; margin-top: 10pt"><B>Item&nbsp;2. Description of Property</B>
</DIV>


<DIV align="justify" style="font-size: 10pt; margin-top: 10pt; text-indent: 8%">The office is located in Livingston Corporate Park in Livingston, New Jersey. The Company
leases approximately 6,300 square feet of office space, the lease term expires June&nbsp;30, 2009 at a
monthly cost of $7,317 which Milestone believes to be competitive. The Company is currently in the
process of reviewing the current lease and negotiating with the landlord for possible extension of
the lease term. The leased office space is in good condition. A third party distribution and
logistics center in Pennsylvania handles shipping and order fulfillment on a month-to-month basis.
</DIV>
<P align="center" style="font-size: 10pt; text-indent: 4%">&nbsp;

<P align="center" style="font-size: 10pt"><!-- Folio -->11<!-- /Folio -->
</DIV>

<!-- PAGEBREAK -->
<P><HR noshade><P>
