believes that there are approximately 2,400 and 2,600 beneficial owners of the Company&#146;s common
stock at December&nbsp;31, 2008 and 2007, respectively.
</DIV>

<DIV align="justify" style="font-size: 10pt; margin-top: 10pt"><B>Dividends</B>
</DIV>


<DIV align="justify" style="font-size: 10pt; margin-top: 10pt; text-indent: 8%">The holders of the Common Stock are entitled to receive such dividends as may be declared by
Milestone&#146;s Board of Directors. Milestone has not paid and does not expect to declare or pay any
dividends in the foreseeable future.
