<DIV style="font-family: 'Times New Roman',Times,serif; margin-left: .25in; width: 7.20in">

<DIV align="justify" style="font-size: 10pt; margin-top: 10pt">The Company has informal arrangements with the manufacturer of the <I>STA</I>, <I>CompuDent </I>and <I>CompuMed</I>
instruments, one of the principal manufacturers of the handpieces and for those instruments
pursuant to which they manufacture these products under specific purchase orders but without any
long-term contract or minimum purchase commitment. Purchases from this supplier were $182,975
(14.5%) and $1,545,000 (42.7%) in 2008 and 2007, respectively. The Company has a manufacturing
agreement with one of the principal manufacturers of the handpieces pursuant to which they
manufacture products under specific purchase orders but without minimum purchase commitments.
Purchases from this supplier for handpieces were $156,698 (12.4%) and $991,626 (27.3%) in 2008 and
2007, respectively. The Company has established an alternate source of supply for the handpieces in
China and other alternate sources of supply exist. Purchases of handpieces from China represent one
supplier. Purchases from this supplier were $920,267 (73.0%) and $1,032,313 (28.4%) in 2008 and
2007, respectively. All other purchases from other suppliers were not significant in either 2008 or
2007.
</DIV>

<DIV align="justify" style="font-size: 10pt; margin-top: 10pt">During the years ended December&nbsp;31, 2008 and 2007, Milestone had two customers (distributors)&nbsp;with
each accounting for approximately 81% and 64%, respectively, of its net product sales for the year
ended December&nbsp;31, 2008 and 2007, respectively. Accounts receivable from these two customers
amounted to approximately $865,000 (79%) and $391,000 (79%) of gross accounts receivable at
December&nbsp;31, 2008 and 2007.
</DIV>

<DIV align="justify" style="font-size: 10pt; margin-top: 10pt">During 2008 and 2007, respectively, Milestone earned royalty income of $28,282 and $128,105 from
the licensee of Milestone&#146;s proprietary consumer dental whitening product, which is sold under
Milestone&#146;s distributor&#146;s trademark, <I>Ionic White</I>. &#151; See Note N (6)&nbsp;Subsequent Events.
</DIV>

<DIV align="justify" style="font-size: 10pt; margin-top: 10pt"><B>NOTE N &#151; COMMITMENTS AND OTHER</B>
