per annum which was amended in April&nbsp;2004 to extend the lease expiration date through June&nbsp;30,
2009. This lease provides for escalations of Milestone&#146;s share of utilities and operating expenses.
Milestone also leases office and telecom equipment under operating leases with payments ranging
from $71-$522 per month.
